WEBVTT

00:00:00.050 --> 00:00:45.250
Subtitle Provide by dramacool.in Translator [Admin.@YNG]

00:00:50.625 --> 00:00:51.666
One day ago

00:00:51.958 --> 00:00:53.625
I parted ways with Li Jingnian and the others

00:00:53.875 --> 00:00:55.541
and came alone to Lonely Inscription Villa

00:00:55.958 --> 00:00:59.125
Back then, I had no idea I would die here

00:01:01.041 --> 00:01:02.833
Open the door! Let me out!

00:01:02.958 --> 00:01:03.916
Let me out!

00:01:04.000 --> 00:01:05.208
The killer is outside

00:01:07.166 --> 00:01:08.416
Let me out!

00:01:18.541 --> 00:01:20.750
Don’t you want to know who the murderer is?

00:01:21.250 --> 00:01:22.708
If you kill me

00:01:23.041 --> 00:01:24.333
you’ll all die too

00:01:41.291 --> 00:01:43.458
Master, this is our grand gift for you

00:01:44.416 --> 00:01:46.083
Good, very good

00:01:59.583 --> 00:02:01.250
The victim’s body is thin

00:02:01.416 --> 00:02:02.750
Multiple bone fractures

00:02:03.458 --> 00:02:06.291
He must have suffered abuse before death

00:02:06.708 --> 00:02:09.833
Two fatal stab wounds to the chest

00:02:31.666 --> 00:02:33.416
The wounds are so subtle

00:02:33.500 --> 00:02:35.958
which means the toxin is extremely potent

00:02:36.791 --> 00:02:40.166
It seems the cause of death may not be the stab wounds

00:02:48.666 --> 00:02:49.625
Who are you?

00:02:50.666 --> 00:02:53.541
I am Lian Songbai, heir of the Lian Family

00:02:53.583 --> 00:02:56.291
I’ve come with my wife to celebrate my mentor’s birthday

00:02:57.333 --> 00:02:58.625
Did you kill him?

00:02:59.250 --> 00:03:00.416
I didn’t

00:03:02.833 --> 00:03:04.625
Only one of you can live

00:03:04.750 --> 00:03:06.958
Whoever tells the truth will survive

00:03:08.333 --> 00:03:09.791
If my husband dies

00:03:10.333 --> 00:03:12.000
I won’t live alone either

00:03:13.208 --> 00:03:15.666
I, Gao Li, am a renowned and upright scholar

00:03:16.500 --> 00:03:18.083
I could never do such a thing

00:03:18.208 --> 00:03:20.250
My adoptive father is a high official in the capital

00:03:20.458 --> 00:03:23.541
I can give you anything you want

00:03:28.416 --> 00:03:30.291
Just say if you killed him or not

00:03:30.333 --> 00:03:31.000
I...

00:03:40.666 --> 00:03:42.000
What are you doing?

00:03:46.666 --> 00:03:48.875
Young Hero Lin is also a guest

00:03:49.083 --> 00:03:51.666
Master, he drugged us first and knocked us out

00:03:51.750 --> 00:03:53.666
Then he interrogated us like criminals

00:03:53.791 --> 00:03:55.291
Luckily, Butler Wang arrived

00:03:55.541 --> 00:03:57.041
I was just investigating the case

00:03:57.500 --> 00:03:58.333
I didn’t do anything to you

00:03:58.333 --> 00:03:59.875
Besides, you tied me up too, so we’re even

00:04:00.166 --> 00:04:00.666
It’s over

00:04:00.708 --> 00:04:02.916
Alright, you all go back now

00:04:03.583 --> 00:04:05.791
No one is allowed to mention today’s events

00:04:12.708 --> 00:04:13.625
Young Hero Lin

00:04:14.541 --> 00:04:16.291
Sorry you had to suffer

00:04:18.125 --> 00:04:21.458
I have some reputation in the literary circles

00:04:22.333 --> 00:04:26.666
It must be a prank by some old rival

00:04:27.583 --> 00:04:29.083
Let’s just forget about it

00:04:29.875 --> 00:04:30.750
Wang Zheng

00:04:31.250 --> 00:04:33.500
Go bury the body quickly

00:04:33.583 --> 00:04:35.041
Yes, Master

00:04:40.166 --> 00:04:42.250
Let’s leave it at that

00:04:52.750 --> 00:04:54.166
I know your death was unjust

00:04:56.458 --> 00:04:58.500
But you’ve been gone for so many years

00:05:00.000 --> 00:05:01.541
Just rest in peace

00:05:05.500 --> 00:05:06.708
Teng Rong

00:05:38.916 --> 00:05:40.291
Something's wrong.

00:05:41.500 --> 00:05:43.916
They're definitely hiding something.

00:05:44.500 --> 00:05:46.250
They have a connection to that unidentified corpse.

00:05:46.333 --> 00:05:48.250
There's no way they're not involved.

00:05:55.583 --> 00:05:58.041
Madam, it's time to get up.

00:06:04.458 --> 00:06:06.083
A ghost! A ghost!

00:06:11.000 --> 00:06:12.125
What's going on?

00:06:17.166 --> 00:06:18.333
What's happening?

00:06:19.208 --> 00:06:20.916
That's the pot calling the kettle black.

00:06:21.666 --> 00:06:24.083
I think you killed Teng Rong.

00:06:25.291 --> 00:06:27.916
There are only a few of us in Lonely Inscription Villa.

00:06:28.583 --> 00:06:30.375
Except for you, the outsider.

00:06:33.750 --> 00:06:35.208
Young Master Gao Li,

00:06:35.708 --> 00:06:37.000
You might want to think again.

00:06:37.333 --> 00:06:40.000
There's also an unidentified male corpse here.

00:06:41.000 --> 00:06:44.458
What if Teng Rong wasn't killed by a person?

00:06:44.916 --> 00:06:46.250
What do you mean by that?

00:06:47.083 --> 00:06:48.333
Young Hero Lin,

00:06:49.666 --> 00:06:51.875
What are you implying?

00:06:52.916 --> 00:06:53.833
Old Master,

00:06:54.666 --> 00:06:57.708
Actually, I ran into Teng Rong last night.

00:06:57.916 --> 00:06:59.208
He told me

00:06:59.458 --> 00:07:02.625
there's a vengeful ghost that's haunted this villa for years.

00:07:02.833 --> 00:07:04.125
The ghost told him

00:07:04.583 --> 00:07:06.375
he won't spare anyone present.

00:07:08.958 --> 00:07:10.166
No one.

00:07:12.500 --> 00:07:13.875
From this moment on,

00:07:14.000 --> 00:07:16.083
I've realized everyone is hiding something.

00:07:16.500 --> 00:07:17.833
Teng Rong's death

00:07:18.083 --> 00:07:19.958
is only the beginning.